value:
I'm not just the daughter of the great
King Anankos, I'm his most loyal
servant. I live only to obey him!

There is another me in this world?
Well, that's just a distraction. If she
tries to stand in my way, I'll end her.

Corrin? Corrin... Ugh. Why does that
name make my heart hurt?

You're a fool! You're a coward! And a
fool! You wear your heart on your
sleeve! I can't stand you!

Anyone stupid enough to follow that
fake King Anankos will end up the
same as him: dead.

Only fools seek close friends. Fools
like the false King Anankos. Are you a
fool? Like $Nf?

There's no point trying to resist the
great King Anankos. I'll gladly beat
that into your stupid skull if I have to.

You were meant to die here. It's fun
to watch you struggle—you can't
escape your fate.
Well... This is unpleasant.

With this power...with this power I
can cut down all who dare stand
in his way!

I am Lilith, daughter of King Anankos.
My blood is of the true Silent Dragon,
and I'll snuff out any who resist him.

You may think that it was your power
that summoned me here,
$Nu...$k$pBut that is far from true. I'm here
because the great King Anankos
imposed his will through you.$k$pThis means, of course, that you
cannot command me like you would
the other so-called Heroes.$k$pNo. I'll take my time and judge your
strengths and weaknesses for myself.
Then we'll see.$k$pSo you should probably avoid letting
any stupid notions like "trust" or
"friendship" into your head, got it?
たっ
てやっ
きゃっ…
馬鹿な…
A disgusting fake...
I like that look of despair...
Do you wish to die?
I will annihilate you!
Fa...ther...
(Chuckle)
I am Lilith. Daughter, and most loyal servant, of the great King Anankos.
Hmph! I despise jokes. Take them elsewhere.
Impersonating Anankos... Despicable.
Foolish humans...  Did you really think you could beat me?
Why can't I make the final blow...? I must carry out my mission!
I've...never known love...
You are inferior to King Anankos...but I will do as you say.
Fine.
Where?
If I must.
